extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  h3 Welcome to #[em Vinyl Inventory]!

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The inventory currently consists of:

    ul
      li #[strong Vinyls:] !{data.vinyl_count}
      li #[strong Vinyls available:] !{data.vinyl_available_count}
      li #[strong Artists:] !{data.artist_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}